The [[Konkani]] language spoken in the Indian state of [[Goa]] has [[loanwords]] from multiple languages, including [[Arabic language|Arabic]], [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]], [[English language|English]] and [[Hindi]]. This is a '''list of loanwords in the Konkani language'''.
